    <scopecontent>
    <head>Descriptive Entry</head>
     <p>This accession consists of correspondence, memoranda, questionnaires, minutes of meetings, metrication reports, a proposed worklist for the Interagency Committee on 
    Metric Policy, news releases, U. S. Metric Board records, summary reports, and brochures. Materials also include agenda listings, American National Metric Council Conference 
    records, a directory of attendees, metric measurement information, and state/regional status reports. Most of the records were created and maintained by John F. Jameson.</p> </scopecontent> 
     
     
 
    
    
    
    
        
